  "description": "<p>\n\tone(1), two(2), three(3), four(4), five(5), six(6), seven(7)...ten(10)，从1-10的数字念法最是容易不过了，初学英语者都能顺利地念出来。</p>\n<p>\n\t同样的，从11-99，对广大英语学习者来说也不难，只要熟练掌握各种十位和各位的数词念法，读的时候&rdquo;十位+个位&ldquo;就可以了。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>个位：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201603/f107583199bf4002a8e3adace488dbc8.jpg\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>十位：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201603/be217207b9a74909a1098395338ca453.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t按照&rdquo;十位+个位&ldquo;的方法读数，如：31 thirty-one, 56 fifty-six, 82 eighty-two</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>注意：在书写中，十位和个位中间要加上连字符&rdquo;-&ldquo;</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>三位数的读法：</strong>在百位和十位（若无十位，则和个位）之间，记得在读的时候，一定要加上and！加上and！加上and！</p>\n<p>\n\t如：106 one hundred <span style=\"color: #f00;\">and</span> six &nbsp; 123 one hundred <span style=\"color: #f00;\">and</span> twenty-three</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 110 one hundred <span style=\"color: #f00;\">and</span> ten &nbsp; 157 one hundred <span style=\"color: #f00;\">and</span> fifty-seven</p>\n<p>\n\t在英文中，没有&rdquo;万&ldquo;这个概念，如果我们想表达&rdquo;一万&ldquo;，就要说成&rdquo;ten thousand&quot;(十千=一万）；如果想表达&ldquo;二十万&rdquo;，就要说成&ldquo;two hundred thousand&quot;（两百千=二十万），对于中国人来说，这实在是太别扭了，不过，歪果仁就是这么念的。而且，一不小心，就会念错或者直接不会念。这里教给大家一个方法：</p>\n<p>\n\t先记住这几个数位：千（thousand）1000；</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;百万（million）100,000；&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;十亿（billion）100,000,000</p>\n<p>\n\t所以，遇到一个三位数以上的数字，先从后往前，每三位用逗号隔开，再去准确地读出来</p>\n<p>\n\t看几个例子，大家就明白了：</p>\n<p>\n\te.g. 2847&rarr;<span style=\"color: #f00;\">2</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">847</span>:<span style=\"color: #f00;\"> two thousand</span> <span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">eight hundred and forty-seven</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">e.g. 35262</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&rarr;<span style=\"color: #f00;\">35</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">262</span>:<span style=\"color: #f00;\"> thirty-five thousand</span> <span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">two hundred and sixty-two</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">e.g. 843691</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&rarr;<span style=\"color: #f00;\">843</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">691</span>: <span style=\"color: #f00;\">eighty hundred and forty-three thousand</span> <span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">six hundred and ninety-one</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">e.g. 2846215</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">2</span>,<span style=\"color: #f00;\">846</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">215</span>: <span style=\"color: #008000;\">two million</span> <span style=\"color: #f00;\">eight hundred and forty-six thousand </span><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">two hundred and fifteen</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">e.g. 36489246</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">36</span>,<span style=\"color: #f00;\">489</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">246</span>: <span style=\"color: #008000;\">thirty-six million</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #f00;\">four hundred and eighty-nine thousand</span> <span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">two hundred and forty-six&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">e.g. 2189456374</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\">2</span>,<span style=\"color: #008000;\">189</span>,<span style=\"color: #f00;\">456</span>,<span style=\"color: #0000cd;\">374</span>: <span style=\"color: #ff8c00;\">two billion</span> <span style=\"color: #008000;\">one hundred and eight-nine million</span> <span style=\"color: #f00;\">four hundred and fifty-six thousand</span><span style=\"color: #0000cd;\"> three hundred and seventy-four</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t例子就举到这里，数字越长读的时候就越要仔细。什么？你连数词的拼写都没有把握，比如90到底是ninty 还是 ninety？那先去补补课吧！<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p766315/\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;&gt;1-100的英文数字，你真的都能拼对吗？</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.8em;\">声明：本文系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p769628/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p769628\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769555/\">跟我是歌手学英文：See You Again</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769290/\">《太阳的后裔》 大热时：撩妹撩汉英文咋说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769419/\">《疯狂动物城》里的地道趣语，你get了吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p745064/\">孙俪邓超变脸：当高颜值明星脸混搭在一起</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768387/\">6个励志小故事 快乐就是这么简单(4)</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769565/\">全世界最孤单的企鹅：这个背影让你看得想哭</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769510/\">泰国高颜值拉面店：你们是卖面啊还是卖肉啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p359145/\">美女翻译张璐：6年总理答记者会精彩翻译集</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p769582/\">权力的游戏精读：信念破灭英文怎么说？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/